{"tid":2289274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"恐怖！睡醒驚見「蒼白女鬼對他笑」網友目睹驚：她也在我家","createTime":"2020-11-17T06:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T09:27:43.000Z","uid":25468,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62d36fd8ebb8e261331d601b12f3859b37f2f659","tid":2289274,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T06:57:48.000Z","msg":"一覺醒來，準備迎接美好的一天，卻當場被眼前的「恐怖景象」嚇瘋！近日一名日本網友在推特發文表示，自己睡醒後，突然發現房間的玻璃門浮現出一張「女鬼的臉」，且對著他淺笑，讓他當場嚇壞，真相曝光後引起網友熱烈討論，不少人直呼「她也出現在我家」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/17/2886355-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F17%2F2886355-PH.jpg&h=4662a27b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本網友睡醒，被玻璃門上浮現的「女鬼臉」嚇壞。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本媒體報導，14日一名推特帳號「っばさ」的網友PO出一張照片，表示自己睡醒後被眼前出現的一幕給嚇傻，從原PＯ貼出的照片可見，<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">正對他的房間玻璃門底下浮現一張「女鬼的臉」</span></strong>，可以看到那張蒼白的臉平躺在地板上，不但透過玻璃門直視著他，甚至還露出一抹淺笑，讓他看了冷汗直流，下一秒才發現原來是虛驚一場。<br />\n<br />\n仔細一看，原來玻璃門對面根本沒有什麼女鬼，而是連鎖咖啡店「星巴克」紙袋上印的商標圖案（女海妖），由於紙袋被橫放在玻璃門外，因此才會讓原PO看錯，以為在房間裡看到「靈異畫面」。<br />\n<br />\n照片一出，立刻引起大批網友熱議，至今已吸引近40萬人按讚，不少人看完後全笑翻，紛紛表示「嚇我一跳，我還以為真的看到鬼」、「笑死我了」、「起床看到這個真的會嚇死」、「如果是我看到絕對尖叫」、「我也常常亂丟紙袋然後被嚇到」、「我家一堆紙袋，我有相同的經驗」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/17/2886352-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F17%2F2886352-PH.jpg&h=6f59b7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲原來玻璃門外不是「女鬼的臉」，而是星巴克的袋子。"},{"pid":"b68ab4a388b1ce3224f9980f4040410c2b7058b9","tid":2289274,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"幫襯藍店，屌你老母"},{"pid":"526a078b7e4839e40e972041ac0ae751da3cfa52","tid":2289274,"uid":41246,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b68ab4a388b1ce3224f9980f4040410c2b7058b9","tid":2289274,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"幫襯藍店，屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"日本starbucks係藍店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19846443548001678ba3a4e2d14e5102f0bf64d","tid":2289274,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"咁大個袋，買左d咩？"},{"pid":"d433b59410cdda8e3b89d1a2a35cbc7f5664d275","tid":2289274,"uid":131884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b68ab4a388b1ce3224f9980f4040410c2b7058b9","tid":2289274,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"幫襯藍店，屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"cctai既水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcff372bc2107e25e44f5de83b0249ce155cfa8","tid":2289274,"uid":213367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b68ab4a388b1ce3224f9980f4040410c2b7058b9","tid":2289274,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"幫襯藍店，屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:43:00.000Z","msg":"腦唔係咁難用㗎喎"},{"pid":"0d9d2ea3c2370e985bac416247ab123041ddbd00","tid":2289274,"uid":65612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b68ab4a388b1ce3224f9980f4040410c2b7058b9","tid":2289274,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"幫襯藍店，屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9d163b13fb1c0f139386de30f36bf73847d9be","tid":2289274,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddcff372bc2107e25e44f5de83b0249ce155cfa8","tid":2289274,"uid":213367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b68ab4a388b1ce3224f9980f4040410c2b7058b9","tid":2289274,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"幫襯藍店，屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:43:00.000Z","msg":"腦唔係咁難用㗎喎"},"citedBy":0,"